cricksmtgravatt.com.au ON SITE BANK FINANCE FACILITIES
"Terms and conditions Cricks Mt Gravatt's end of financial year period campaign encompasses the months May & June 2017 and will offer discounts of up to $8,000 off the recommended drive away price of new, demonstrator & used vehicle stock. The total number of new, demonstrator & used vehicles to which this offer applies
is greater than 100. The Cricks Mt Gravatt EOFYS Advantage package is a tailor made financial product, available to eligible purchasers of new, demonstrator & used vehides. Regulatory lending and eligibility criteria, terms and conditions apply. Eligible purchasers, who qualify for the Cricks Mt Gravatt Advantage financial product
package, will receive: The lender's lowest fixed interest rate for the term of the loan. New & demonstrator vehicles eligible under the Cricks Mt Gravatt EOFYS Advantage will receive 2 years of scheduled services free of charge, according to the manufacturer's recommendations. Purchasers of used vehides eligible under the Cricks
Advantage will receive a Cricks Mt Gravatt service department voucher to the value of $1,000 - this amount is equal to the average cost of the first 2 years' servicing cost for new & demonstrator vehides. The first year's comprehensive motor vehicle insurance valued up to $850. Insurance value cannot be credited to any other offer
or used as further discount if purchasers decide to not proceed with offered insurance. Customers who choose to obtain their own financing are free to negotiate on the price of the vehicle as per normal commercial terms. Finance offers by the vehicle manufacturer do not form part of Cricks Mit Gravatt EOFYS Advantage package
as these are Manufacturer offers and have different terms and conditions. Terms and conditions available in-store or cricks.com.au. Offer available to obble purchasers of new. demo and used vehides in stock Vehides must be sold and delivered between 10/4/2017 and 30/6/2017.
